            </div><h2 id="基本用法">基本用法</h2>
<ol>
<li>
<p>一般對應</p>
<ul>
<li><code>var mapper = Mapper.Map&lt;TargetType&gt;(customer);</code></li>
<li><code>var mapper = Mapper.Map&lt;FromType, TargetType&gt;(customer);</code></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p>客製化對應</p>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
